- 📝 Structured logging with slog
- 🐳 Docker and docker-compose ready
- 🔄 Hot reload with [Air](https://github.com/cosmtrek/air)
- ✅ Health check endpoints (`/health`, `/ready`, `/live`)
- 🔒 CORS middleware configured
- 📊 Request logging middleware

## Prerequisites

- Go {{goVersion}} or higher
- Docker (optional)
- [Air](https://github.com/cosmtrek/air) for hot reload (optional)

## Getting Started

### Install dependencies

```bash
go mod download
```

### Run in development mode

```bash
# With hot reload
make dev

# Or without hot reload
make run
```

### Run tests

```bash
make test
```

### Build for production

```bash
make build
# or for static binary
make build-static
```

### Run with Docker

```bash
# Build image
make docker-build

# Run container
make docker-run

# Or use docker-compose
docker-compose up -d
```

